            <title>[CASSANDRA-3826] Pig cannot use output formats other than CFOF</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3826</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Pig has ColumnFamilyOutputFormat hard coded.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
